sys_hub_action_type_definition.description:
This action provide info about epics by passing following inputs.

Inputs Name-

  • Id of Release(Mandatory)

 Outputs epics – object with data for epics.

  • Id-Id of epic
  • Name-Name of epic
  • Created At-Created date/time of epic
  • Url-url of epic
  • Resource-resource of epic
  • Ref Num:ref num of epic
  • Product Id:id of product
